# Signatures and Security

## Page Signatures

Jaringan supports ed25519 digital signatures for page authenticity.

## Keyring

Keys are stored in `~/.config/jaringan/keyring`:

```
my-server ed25519:BASE64PUBLICKEY...
```

## Signed Pages

```
~~~~~
title: Signed Document
signed-by: my-server
signature: ed25519:BASE64SIGNATURE...
```

## Verification

The browser shows signature status in the header.

